WEBVTT

00:03:27.075 --> 00:03:30.319
So we started to work our way
down the list.

00:03:31.167 --> 00:03:34.169
I'm just one of many entrepreneurs,

00:03:34.193 --> 00:03:36.775
and we are just one of many start-ups

00:03:36.799 --> 00:03:39.660
trying to fix what's wrong with news.

00:03:39.684 --> 00:03:41.630
All of us in the trenches know

00:03:41.654 --> 00:03:44.129
that something is wrong
with the news industry.

00:03:44.153 --> 00:03:45.368
It's broken.

00:03:46.556 --> 00:03:49.903
Trust in the media
has hit an all-time low.

00:03:49.927 --> 00:03:53.322
And the statistic you're seeing up there
is from September --

00:03:53.346 --> 00:03:55.342
it's arguably gotten worse.

00:03:56.104 --> 00:03:57.576
But we can fix this.

00:03:57.600 --> 00:03:59.318
We can fix the news.